00:06:34.190 --> 00:06:36.880
I have B inverse
times A A inverse.

00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:37.780
That's the identity.

00:06:37.780 --> 00:06:39.640
So that's my B inverse.

00:06:39.640 --> 00:06:43.180
And I have the minus, the B
