00:07:17.310 --> 00:07:19.440
Everywhere here, I'm
assuming that A and B

00:07:19.440 --> 00:07:21.300
are invertible matrices.

00:07:21.300 --> 00:07:24.300
So when I multiply by
an invertible matrix,

00:07:24.300 --> 00:07:26.530
